summary: Request: KamiJirou; Monster AU, Kaminari as a mad scientist bringing his Frankenstein monster Jirou to life
question: Request: KamiJirou; Monster AU, Kaminari as a mad scientist bringing his Frankenstein monster Jirou to life
answer:
“RISE, RISE, MY CREATION! IT’S ALIVE! IT’S ALIVE! MWAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA!”

The creature groaned and slowly got up from the table its body had been resting on while Dr. Kaminari gazed at her with glee. Truly a masterpiece.

“Greetings, creature. I am Dr. Denki Awesomeness Kaminari, your creator,” he said, introducing himself, “the world’s greatest mad scientist and yes, Awesomeness is my middle name, I gave it to myself. What do you-”

He got no further when the creature clocked him through the wall. Denki was fine. Shaken and scraped, but fine. Possibly a little turned on by the monster he had just created.

What he hadn’t realized as he had put together the parts for the creature was how stunning the creation would look. Or that it was a woman.

Denki coughed as he straightened his goggles and dusted himself off. “Apologies, creature, I was just asking which name you would like to be called.”

The creature smiled, twirling her earphone jacks as she looked down at the human. She was going to enjoy this one very much.

“Call me Jirou, master. Kyouka Jirou.”

____________________

As for the todomomo request in my inbox, I’ll get to it after fluff week and my E3 2019 post, so stay tuned, whoever requested that one!

Feedback is appreciated!

Until then!
